plot: Nombre Original: Bugs Bunny: Baseball BugsDirector: Tex Avery, Friz FrelengActores: Bugs BunnyA baseball game is going on in New York City, at the Polo Grounds (although the rooftop facade is more suggestive of Yankee Stadium), between the visiting "Gas-House Gorillas" and the home team, the "Tea Totallers".
